Description: 21dao is a non profit organization supporting artists on Solana and 21dao.xyz is our first community driven project. 21dao aggregates live auction and secondary data from the top 1/1 marketplaces on Solana (Exchange, Holaplex, and Formfunction).

With 3moji, users can finally have control over how their NFT looks. Users start by minting a "base layer" and an accessory in order to combine them together to generate a “Meta NFT”. If you want to upgrade your avatar and change your look, you can simply sell the old accessory on the secondary market and that would reflect on your Meta NFT.
4Site is a decentralised social media platform based on the solana network. Using blockchain technology, users create accounts that are minted as NFTs.
Abas makes it easy for anyone to execute complex market-neutral trading strategies across Solana decentralized exchanges

There are massive arbitrage opportunities across lending protocols. We saw that hundreds of millions of dollars are earning sub-optimal rates, and the user experience is complicated. We built a flexible smart contract that aggregates these opportunities. It can allocate funds to multiple protocols at once and theoretically integrate with dozens of protocols, circumventing Solana's transaction limits while being decentralized.

Acumen’s Vision is to enable fair access to capital for small and medium-sized businesses and entrepreneurs in developing nations (microfinance) by bridging crypto and traditional assets.The Acumen StableDapp will use stablecoin deposits in crypto to give out microfinance credits to such business, while enabling the users to generate a stable uncorrelated yield.
Advent is the first fixed-rate borrow/lend protocol with concentrated liquidity. It allows for creating fixed-rate deposits or loans with any maturity, drawing from a single, central pool of capital.
Akura brings permissionless, tokenized index funds & ETFs to Solana.
Allwin is a decentralized savings protocol on Solana. Allwin contains two parts: no-loss lottery & no-loss prediction market.

Amulet Protocol is a decentralized insurance protocol built for the Rust-based ecosystem, starting with the Solana blockchain. Amulet has designed an innovative and open insurance model, which not only effectively addresses the common challenges of existing decentralized insurance protocols, but also creates a new paradigm shift for the whole insurance sector. Amulet is creating the industry’s first Protocol-Controlled Underwriting (PCU) approach, in which Amulet will build up its own underwriting capabilities and introduce a claim structure involving a unique Yield Backed Claim (YBC) method.
Anatoly The Cat is an NFT top trumps game.
Apostro is a risk management platform that prevents economical smart contract exploits by enforcing safe economical restrictions
Arena is an onchain gaming platform.
ArtyFracts aims to crowd-fund a real world art masterpiece purchase and decentralise the ownership via NFTs.
Aten is a marketplace that enables merchants and NFT projects to utilize Solana Pay as a form of payment.
ATIV activates music copyright in the form of NFTs. Music becomes more valuable through decentralized/distributed ownership.

Audience Protocol's vision is to define a simple, decentralized model of the Creator / Audience relationship that is provably tamper proof, and then rebuild the entire online content industry on top of it. We're starting with a simple Patronage business model built on top of the protocol but are driving towards a world where millions of teams and people are building new, innovative services and business models on top of the protocol that empower and protect creators to freely express themselves.
Auzimons is a 100% on-chain NFT card game.
Awaken is a trustless automation protocol, we built that because current transactions on blockchain are settled instantaneous but most real-world transactions occur after conditions are met.

Badbeat poker club is a decentralised, NFT fuelled, open source, poker community where the value is grown and retained by the community itself. Allowing its members to play and earn in a fun and safe environment. Whilst being rewarded with our native FIRE utility token, governance token, NFT’s and much more.
Banana Wallet is a Solana wallet for easy micropayments.

Bidali enables people to buy gift cards and mobile airtime we're able to quickly and easily enable people to convert the value locked in stablecoins into tangible things at thousands of brands worldwide without extra costs.
Biddi is the first Solana p2p exchange built on the Anchor framework.
No-code analytics for programs, solve a common pain point.

We are building a platform for DAOs, where any DAO can create an event of NFT bonding. The main purpose of these events is to provide a possibility for DAOs to request some NFTs from collections they are interested in and to offer DAO's locked-up tokens for these NFTs.
Boom is a permissionless sports betting protocol built on Solana.

Boost Protocol is an asset management protocol built using Blade Labs vault infrastructure. The primary offering of the Boost Protocol are Boosted Vaults. These vaults implement an automated recursive deposit-borrow strategy in order to increase yield on vault denominated assets.
Bounty Bot is here to organize the bounty ecosystem in Web3, in a trustless and transparent way.

Every day at 1pm, users join and answer 12 trivia questions. Players who answer all questions correctly split a prize fund sponsored by advertisers. The questions are written about general encyclopedic topics, not about crypto. You need to set up a crypto wallet to play. Every question answer is a transaction. The payouts are sent with USDC.

Bucket protocol builds an aggregation layer on top of existing stablecoins across Solana to create a canonical mint for a USD-pegged token on Solana. Bucket offers a unifying stablecoin interface to trading protocols and additional liquidity to stableswap protocols, whereas consumers benefit from a diversified stablecoin index with an insurance fund and automated yield that simplifies participation in DeFi into a one-step process.
A base protocol for tradable on-chain subscriptions.

Cafeteria.gg is an innovative chat platform natively infused with the latest crypto-tech to bring a new and exciting community driven experience. It was built to bridge web2 users to the web3 world in a fun, safe, and social environment, and also allow users to monetize their engagement and communities.
Calcifer is a DeFi protocol that allows for the creation of synthetic tokens that represent the future yield of a deposit.
A work coordination protocol, the first use-case for memes.

Candy Shop is a tool suite that enables anyone to launch their own NFT marketplace within a few minutes! Built on the Metaplex Auction House and the Candy Shop on-chain program, Candy Shop SDK is an open source Javascript library that comes with key functional commands and data endpoints for hosting your own NFT marketplace.

Cardinal protocol provides a way to wrap NFTs with time and usage based expiry. Owners/issuers can issue their NFTs as rentals with custom invalidation parameters including price and duration. Borrowers/renters can pay to claim an available rental from the marketplace pool, and after the specified amount of time has expired, the NFT will be programmatically revoked from their wallet and returned to the owner.

Cassava is the crypto infrastructure in Africa. It aims to empower billions of African users with Web3 technologies by providing users with a series of products such as multichain wallet, NFT marketplace, crypto-based rewards system, DID (digital identity) and OATs (on-chain achievement token) system, etc.

Here at CellFi, CLOB liquidity is wrapped into farms and defi users could easily provide liq for CLOB. We have multiple strategies that helps get really high yield with moderate risk. CellFi farms is the first yielding pool that helps you generate profit directly from volatility.
We built this project because the future is multi-chain. Solana will live side by side Ethereum, Tezos, Hedera Hashgraph, and many more.
Chat3 is a messaging application that uses decentralized principles and also peer-to-peer as real-time communication.

Check Protocol is a protocol that going to provide Solana with an interoperable trust layer solution for decentralized identities and verifiable credentials that can be implemented in numerous use-cases.
An online chess game on the Solana blockchain. You need to buy NFT chess pieces and bet one of them before playing.
CHESSFi is a web3 based chess with GameFi and LearnFi elements.

Circles DAO is the platform for creative content creators where people can collaborate using DAO. Creators can create content and sell it as NFT’s and blind boxes and can share the rewards among the DAO members.
Tipping for Twitch and Twitter on Solana.

City of Legends aims to build a new Solana-based blockchain gaming ecosystem to create more exciting content for gamers around the world, and provide extension opportunities to independent game studios to enter the blockchain world.

Clubverse is a web3 platform for creators and their communities. Users can access exclusive communities with limited edition NFTs. Creators can offer all sorts of perks and services directly from the platform to their users, or open them up to the public.
Coherence Finance provides the ability to buy, sell, or build your own crypto ETFs.
Making day-to-day payments in India using USDC over Solana & UPI (0 MDR) network.
Colatto is a decentralized and open source no loss lottery platform.

Commerce DAO is a fully integrated web3 commerce payment stack powered on Solana. Commerce DAO will also bring innovative solutions to commerce challenges including payment disputes, incentive rewards for loyal customers.
Contribute is where builders coordinate to shape the next generation of the web.
Cooperaty with Cooperaty DAO is the home of a community of Traders, Investors & Students. We want to provide the possibility to anyone to know how to trade.
CoralCube is an NFT marketplace and aggregator that aims to highlight three columns of web3 in the context of NFTs

Crema Finance is a powerful concentrated liquidity protocol that provides superior performance for both traders and liquidity providers. It deployed the first concentrated liquidity market maker (CLMM) algorithm on Solana mainnet that allows users to add liquidity within their specified price ranges. Crema aims to redefine the capital efficiency and trading depth in non-evm ecosystems through both its CLMM infrastructure and a series of affiliate innovations such as NFT liquidity farming, smart router, etc.

Cronos is a task scheduler for Solana with an on-chain task queue where users can schedule instructions to be signed and validated according to a predetermined schedule. These tasks are currently being cranked by an open bot network.

Crosslink Protocol establishes a new web3 primitive 'microtitles' which are NFTs that are cryptographically and incontrovertibly "linked" to a physical item, thereby proffering proof of ownership, and authenticity all-in-one. The system may be used for digitizing assets, and counterfeit prevention.

Crossmint is an SDK for NFT creators and marketplaces to accept credit card payments. It enables anyone to mint an NFT in 1 minute by using their gmail and credit card. No crypto or wallet required - we create one for the user when they mint!

CryptoJobs.network is a permissionless social platform that contains elements of a job board and a social network with a unique feature (Proof of Completion) that allows implementing a decentralized Reputation system, which can be used in later extensions and in any trustless app.
CryptoPay is a merchant gateway dedicated to retail shops and merchants, users can leverage crypto for hard cash just like an ATM. Using our dApp users can pay using barcode and SNS type services.
d’Art uses Solana blockchain technology for services that issue NFTs and provide DEFI for real art objects.

DAO Talents Club aims to assist DAOs with managing and curating talent by keeping track of activities that happen on our platform that include possible bounty bot integrations, XP Collabs & social Kudos that are exchanged between profiles.
Dappsuite Wallet allows Salesforce customers to send USDC stablecoin payments. They can also collateralize SOL in order to Borrow USDC from Jet Protocol.
Dcaf Drip is an automated DCA protocol that uses a novel vault mechanism to provide configurable and scalable cost averaging strategies.

We, The DSOL DAO Community Members, are seeking to Further Decentralize Solana Via Gamification by creating the necessary incentives to have the vast majority of solanists not only care about it, but actually do something about it.
The Ded.social platform aims to bridge the gap between current centralized social media platforms and decentralized cryptocurrency concepts
DeCommas is a Multi-chain DeFi Automation Layer. However, specifically for Riptide Hackathon we've built the Automated Basis Trading Vault.
Degen Islands is a virtual world in which players can participate in a gold rush, anyone can claim a piece of land - or an island in this case - and own all the resources that lay under their feet.
Decentralised Git Repository that can incentivise developers in open source projects.
Revolutionizing payment and credit score infrastructures.
Delphor is a capital-efficient, oracle-based, multi-point Liquidity Provider and Portfolio Manager protocol for Solana.
DeltaFi is the world’s most efficient and user-friendly intelligent AMM design built for traders, market makers, and liquidity providers.
DePocket is an integrated Defi platform that supports people to manage and invest their assets across multi-chain & multi-wallet.
Loyalty programs will change the way we interact with a business. DigiPets gamifies the loyalty program while educating new adopters.

Disco Protocol is a suite of tools that decentralize the way events are managed. We’re making events funky using Solana.
District3 is the first Augmented Reality platform on Solana.
dockIT is a NFT backed invoice generator and payment gateway created with the integration of Solana Pay.
DoDAOs onboarding platform enables DAOs to create interactive onboarding content in the form of guides.

Dona is a checkout donations platform built on Solana Pay. Using Dona, merchants can set up a checkout donation campaign that smoothly integrates into their existing Solana Pay checkout flow to enable charitable donations.
Dragverse will be a dApp where you as an NFT drag (queen, king, monster, etc.) can live broadcast using Livepeer and earn tips from your followers.
Drip Protocol is a mobile-first trading platform built on top of Serum. We built this to address the UX gap between existing Serum DEXes on Solana and centralized exchanges.
AirDrop tool for Solana with a temporary wallet.

Dual Finance aims to be a base-layer incentization protocol for any crypto project. Decentralized crypto structured product protocol with streaming liquidity for sustained yield generation. Designed atop a breakthrough token reward mechanism and capitally efficient collateral management system.

DXMD is the first virtual care platform built on the blockchain. It is a Web 3.0 Virtual Care, Electronic Health Record, & Medical NFT Platform built on Solana. The platform is designed as a DAO to connect patients, providers, and developers together via HIPAA compliant medical dApps and secure databases.

Hedging interest rate risk in DeFi. Lending is the largest pillar of Defi, many protocols on Solana provide variable interest rate borrowing and lending solutions.
